NAME

DBIx::Class::Storage::DBI::Firebird - Driver for the Firebird RDBMS via DBD::Firebird

DESCRIPTION

This is an empty subclass of DBIx::Class::Storage::DBI::InterBase for use with DBD::Firebird, see that driver for details.
